Application: Cascade Demo
  Description: Test fixture for cascade and restrict on delete behavior
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000001

Identity:
  Scopes are "cascade.view", "cascade.manage", "cascade.delete"
  A "tester" has "cascade.view", "cascade.manage", and "cascade.delete"

Content called "parents":
  Each parent has a name which is text, required
  Anyone with "cascade.view" can view parents
  Anyone with "cascade.manage" can create parents
  Anyone with "cascade.delete" can delete parents

Content called "cascade children":
  Each cascade child has a label which is text, required
  Each cascade child has a parent which references parents, required, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "cascade.view" can view cascade children
  Anyone with "cascade.manage" can create cascade children

Content called "restrict children":
  Each restrict child has a label which is text, required
  Each restrict child has a parent which references parents, required, restrict on delete
  Anyone with "cascade.view" can view restrict children
  Anyone with "cascade.manage" can create restrict children
